(6, 'tuyen_dung', 'Tuyển dụng', '<span style="font-size: medium"><span style="color: rgb(11,67,162)">\r\n<p><span style="color: #ff0000"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman"><span style="font-size: large"><em><strong>Th&ocirc;ng Tin Tuyển Dụng Th&aacute;ng 03/2010<br />\r\n</strong></em></span></span></span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman"><span style="color: rgb(11,67,162)"><em><strong><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><br />\r\nDo nhu cầu <strong><em>mở rộng</em></strong> <strong><em>v&agrave;</em></strong> ph&aacute;t triển mạng lư&oacute;i kinh doanh.C</b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">h&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cần tuyển c&aacute;c vị tr&iacute; như sau:<br />\r\n</b></strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #ff0000"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><strong>1. </strong></span></b></span></span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #666666"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><span style="color: #ff0000"><strong>Trưởng</strong> ph&ograve;ng&nbsp;<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">kinh doanh : L&agrave;m việc tại Đ&agrave; Nẵng</b></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</b></span></span></b><span style="color: #000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><u>Y&ecirc;u Cầu:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</u></b></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">- Tốt nghiệp <strong>đại học, </strong>cao đẳng chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh kinh tế, QTKD...hoặc c&aacute;c chu